<p>Integrating with <code>Data Table</code> plugin. Just add a <code>data-target</code> attribute in the <code>select</code> element, pointing the id of the data table. Example:</p>
<pre class="yondu__code"><code>&lt;select name=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;selectpicker abcom-form abcom-form--min form-control abcom-filter__entries abcom-filter__last&quot; <b>data-target=&quot;#table_id&quot;</b>&gt;</code></pre>
<pre class="yondu__code"><code>&lt;table <b>id=&quot;table_id&quot;</b> class=&quot;abcom abcom-table&quot;&gt;</code></pre>